name: Kimberlyna
description: I love friends and family, I am a lot of fun and make friends easily. I love life, love my family and still have some love to share with a special people. Life can be lonely without someone…I am a person who is very real when it comes to life and its’ issues. Am honest,kind caring, affectionate,good sense of humor,easy going,free thinker,trustworthy and respect the lives of other people…..I’m a woman that is living life as it comes to me. I don’t worry about tomorrow, for it will be here no matter what I do.
